sections.content: Time to get shopping. Terms apply.

faqsItems.questionString: Can I get Undefined products delivered?

sections.content: Yes! You can get Undefined products delivered same-day in as fast as one hour from stores near you using the Instacart app or website.

faqsItems.questionString: How does Instacart same-day delivery work?

sections.content: It's simple. Using the Instacart app or website, shop for products from your store of choice near you. Once you place your order, Instacart will connect you with a personal shopper in your area to shop and deliver your order. Contactless delivery is available with our “Leave at my door” option. You can track your order’s progress and communicate with your shopper every step of the way using the Instacart app or website.

sections.name: place_order_link
sections.content: Learn more about how to place an order here.

faqsItems.questionString: How long does Instacart delivery take?

sections.content:
The best part about Instacart is that you can choose when you would like to schedule your delivery. You can get same-day delivery in as fast as one hour, or choose a dropoff time for later in the day or week to fit your schedule.

To make sure you get your delivery as scheduled, we recommend—

sections.name: list
sections.content:
Turning on notifications for the Instacart app--list-item--
Keeping an eye out for text messages and phone calls from your Instacart shopper--list-item--
Leaving helpful instructions for parking, gate codes, or other clues to find your home.

sections.name: same_day_delivery_link
sections.content: Learn more about Instacart same-day delivery here.

faqsItems.questionString: How does Instacart in-store pickup or curbside pickup work?

sections.content:
Using the Instacart app or website, select a store of your choice near you that offers pickup, select Pickup, and then select your preferred pickup location from which you’d like to place your order.

Then, when you arrive at the store of your choice, use the Instacart app to notify us. Depending on the store, a shopper or store employee will bring the groceries to your car, or you can pick them up at the designated area.

sections.name: curbside_pickup_link
sections.content: Learn more about pickup orders here.

faqsItems.questionString: How much does Instacart delivery or pickup cost?

sections.content: Here's a breakdown of Instacart delivery cost:

sections.name: list
sections.content:
Delivery fees start at $3.99 for same-day orders over $35. Fees vary for one-hour deliveries, club store deliveries, and deliveries under $35.--list-item--
Service fees vary and are subject to change based on factors like location and the number and types of items in your cart. Orders containing alcohol have a separate service fee.--list-item--
Tipping is optional but encouraged for delivery orders. It’s a great way to show your shopper appreciation and recognition for excellent service. 100% of your tip goes directly to the shopper who delivers your order.

With an optional Instacart+ membership, you can get $0 delivery fee* on every order over $35. *Service fees apply.

Instacart pickup cost:

sections.name: list
sections.content:
There may be a “pickup fee” (equivalent to a delivery fee for pickup orders) on your pick up order that is typically $1.99 for non-Instacart+ members. Instacart+ membership waives this like it would a delivery fee.--list-item--
Pick up orders have no service fees, regardless of non-Instacart+ or Instacart+ membership.

sections.name: pricing_link
sections.content: Learn more about Instacart pricing here.

faqsItems.questionString: What happens if an item is out of stock and I need to give specific instructions?

sections.content:
When an item you want is out-of-stock at the store, your shopper will follow your replacement preferences.

You can set item and delivery instructions in advance, as well as chat directly with your shopper while they shop and deliver your items. You can tell the shopper to:

sections.name: list
sections.content:
Find Best Match: By default, your shopper will use their best judgement to pick a replacement for your item.--list-item--
Pick Specific Replacement: You can pick a specific alternative for the shopper to purchase if your first choice is out-of-stock.--list-item--
Don't Replace: For items you’d rather not replace, choose “Don't replace” to get a refund if the item is out of stock.

sections.name: oos_link
sections.content: Learn more about instructions for specific items or replacements here.

faqsItems.questionString: What happens if there is an issue with my order?

sections.content: If something isn’t right, you’ve got options. In the Instacart app or website, you can report:

sections.name: list
sections.content:
Missing items--list-item--
Incorrect items--list-item--
Damaged items--list-item--
Poor replacements--list-item--
Early/late orders
If an order never came, or you get someone else’s order, you can reach out to Instacart Customer Experience.
